      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I need some help writing a rejection email. It's for a candidate who made it all the way to the final round for a Senior Dev role here in Austin, but we ended up going with someone who had a bit more experience with AWS architectures. I want to be professional and encouraging because they were actually great, just not the right fit for this specific seniority level right now. Can you give me a draft?",
