    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Thanks, that's a good start. Can you make it a little bit more personal and warm though? Like, I don't want it to feel like a robot sent it. Maybe add a line about how much we actually enjoyed talking to them during the technical interview so they don't feel like they just failed a test?",
